{"article_id":"HugNghri6bzAF1d9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"poster= '' http : //v. .com/images/1155968404/201610/3497/1155968404_5156510889001_5156315187001-vs.jpg","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"? pubId=1155968404 ''","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Off Message","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"5 takeaways from the debate","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that didn ' t matter","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Pence disappoints Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Kaine over-rehearses ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and Quijano whiffs .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"The first and only vice-presidential debate of 2016 was less a game-changer than a channel-changer , a snippy and probably inconsequential 90 minutes","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"marginally won by Mike Pence - a confident , slightly smarmy debater very much in the mold of those","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"calculating Washington , D.C. , politicians","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"who are destroying America .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Tim Kaine , Hillary Clinton ' s more voluble running mate , didn ' t flop","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"but he was visibly less comfortable than the square-jawed Pence ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"frequently interrupting the Indiana governor ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"jamming his pre-programmed attacks on Donald Trump into every answer with admirable , tedious efficiency .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Their performances almost perfectly reflected the priorities of each candidate :","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Kaine was a hyper-briefed Trump-thumping machine ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"barking the GOP nominee ' s name ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"as if it were a slur ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"some 160 times","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"- more than twice the number of times","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"Pence mentioned Clinton ' s ,","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"according a tally .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Pence , on the other hand , seemed less concerned with out-and-out defending his running mate than rope-a-doping away from uncomfortable questions :","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"His standard response was to pucker his face","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"and mock Kaine as \" ridiculous \"","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"for pelting him with facts , statistics and actual Trump quotes .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"if Kaine","depth":15},{"id":30,"text":"( who doesn ' t have an especially close personal relationship with Clinton )","depth":15},{"id":31,"text":"warmly referred to \" Hillary \"","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"as if the two were the best of friends ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"Pence maintained a wary rhetorical distance from Trump .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"He behaved less like an affectionate pal than a guy","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"getting paid","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"to do a job ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"a pet employee","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"reassuring disgruntled co-workers","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that their unpopular boss was actually a great guy , really ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"if only you guys got to know him .","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"In the end you got the sense","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that Pence did as much","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"( maybe more )","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to burnish his own brand than Trump ' s","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"- and","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"even if he ' s widely deemed the winner ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"what lasting good will it do for his undisciplined , self-defeating nominee ?","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Here are five takeaways .","depth":3},{"id":49,"text":"1 . Hillary Clinton is lucky","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"she ' s facing Trump instead of Pence .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Even after having his leonine head handed to him at the first presidential debate last week ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"there ' s no decisive evidence","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that Trump is taking prep for Sunday ' s second round in St. Louis any more seriously","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"than he took prep for the first .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The same can not be said for Pence , a true professional ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"who huddled with Wisconsin Gov . Scott Walker for a week ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and produced a focused performance ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"parrying every attack with a sharp assault on the unholy trinity of Clinton sins :","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"emails , the foundation and her foreign policy failings as secretary of state .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Pence was as un-goad-able","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"as Trump was easily gulled .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"When an aggressive Kaine demanded","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"he defend his running mate ' s comments on everything from declaring Mexican immigrants \" rapists \"","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"to Trump ' s suggestion","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"that the U.S. encourage other countries to develop nukes ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Pence mocked him .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"\" Did you work on that one a long time ?","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Because that had a lot of creative lines in it . \"","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"In the real world outside the Farmville , Va. debate hall , Pence has contradicted or contrasted himself from Trump on any number of issues","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"- most notably his flat refusal","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"to entertain the false assertion","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that President Obama isn ' t a native-born citizen .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"But inside he did a far better job","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"of making Trump ' s case","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"than the candidate has made on his own behalf .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"During his Hofstra meltdown Trump was so occupied","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"defending himself against the self-assured Clinton","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"he forgot his most effective attacks ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"including a much-anticipated hit on the fundraising practices of the Clinton Foundation .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Pence was a cooler customer","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"who calmly went through his head-hunting to-do list .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" While she was secretary of state ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"the Clinton foundation accepted tens of millions of dollars from foreign governments , and foreign donors , ''","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"- precisely the kind of targeted attack","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Trump needs to make","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"in order to recover from his disastrous first debate .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Alec Baldwin studied Trump for weeks","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"to pull off his uncanny impersonation on last week ' s Saturday Night Live .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Trump would be well served to study the YouTube of Pence ' s performance for pointers .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"2 . Tim Kaine wasn ' t trying to win the debate","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"- he was trying to bash Trump .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"The Virginia senator has a reputation","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"for being a nice guy ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"but he was given a hit man ' s job on Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"And the target was Trump , not Pence ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"whom the Clinton campaign regards as a political bit player","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"who will vanish into obscurity after the election .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Hence , Kaine ' s task was a slightly awkward one :","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"to aim over Pence","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and hit Trump .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"It didn ' t really work ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"and not for lack of trying .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"His best moment , arguably , came","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"when he produced a laundry list of awful things","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Trump has said about women , Mexicans and a disabled reporter ;","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"Pence juked","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"and refused to answer","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"- which allowed Kaine to declare :","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"\" He 's refused to defend his running mate . . .","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"and yet , he 's asking everybody to vote for somebody","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"that he can not defend , ''","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"he said in one of the debate ' s few memorable exchanges .","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"But he came off as a bit nervous , like a frustrated school kid","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"trying to disgorge a memorized speech","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"if only his rowdy classmates would allow him to deliver it .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"At times , he seemed peevish .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Pence actually interrupted Kaine a lot ,","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"but his interjections were punchy","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"( often an aspirated \" no ! \"","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"intended to deprive the former Virginia governor a clean sound bite )","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"while Kaine ' s frequent attempts","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"to be heard","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"were of the whiny it ' s-my-turn-to-talk variety","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"which had many viewers","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"( and a focus group","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"convened by GOP pollster Frank Luntz )","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"judging Kaine to be rude .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"3 . Snatching discord from the jaws of victory ?","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"Clinton and her brain trust ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"according to several Democrats","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"I spoke to ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"were satisfied","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"( if not elated )","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"by Kaine ' s performance .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Whether Trump appreciated Pence ' s defenses ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"well that ' s less clear .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"Moments after the candidates left the stage ,","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"John Harwood of CNBC and The New York Times quoted a Trump adviser","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that the GOP nominee ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"who was watching the debate from a hotel in Vegas ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"was less than satisfied with his running mate .","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"\" Pence won overall ,","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"but he didn ' t win with Trump , \"","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"the adviser told Harwood .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"4 . Pence dodged almost every tough question .","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"How do you defend a running mate","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"much of America deems as indefensible ?","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"You don ' t !","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"Trump ' s chorus of validators fanned out this week","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"to declare him a \" genius \"","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"for \" using \" the tax code","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"to avoid paying taxes","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"but the real genius may have been Pence","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"who figured out the best way","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"to answer the thorniest questions about Trump","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"was to respond with an attack on Kaine , or the moderator Elaine Quijano .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"Sure , he answered a handful ,","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"but a tiptoe through the transcript reveals what amounts to a master class in rhetorical deflection .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"When it came to the New York Times story on Trump ' s 1995 New York State tax return","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"- which showed the estate and casino magnate","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"claiming a nearly $ 1 billion loss ,","depth":15},{"id":165,"text":"Pence shrugged his shoulders","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"and repeated the campaign ' s talking-point with televangelistical conviction .","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"\" Donald Trump is a businessman --","depth":15},{"id":168,"text":"he actually built a business , \"","depth":15},{"id":169,"text":"Pence intoned .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"\" Like everybody , he faced some pretty tough times 20 years ago . \"","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"Pence slipped the hook during the most consequential exchange of the night -","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"a tag team onslaught by Kaine and Quijano","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"pressing for Pence to call for Trump to release his tax returns .","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"Quijano , to her credit , repeatedly asked Pence","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"why it was okay for Trump to withhold his filings","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"when the Indiana governor had dutifully released the 10 most recent years of his income statements ;","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"Pence was fumbling for an answer","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"when Kaine ,","depth":17},{"id":179,"text":"who seemed more focused on venting outrage than pinning his quarry ,","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"interrupted her","depth":16},{"id":181,"text":"to make a forgettable point .","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"5 . Quijano was a weak moderator .","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"Tuesday marked the first time","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"a digital division reporter moderated a major debate ,","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"and Quijano","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"- a well-regarded former CNN anchor","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"who now works for CBSN -","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"showed her inexperience .","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"She allowed both candidates to repeatedly interrupt each other ,","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"at times seeming to whisper her questions and demands for decorum .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":381,"left":193,"right":380,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":193,"left":192,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":380,"left":238,"right":379,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":237,"right":48,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":197,"right":236,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":197,"left":194,"right":196,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":5,"right":195,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":195,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":236,"left":204,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":200,"right":203,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":200,"left":8,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":9,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":12,"right":202,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":13,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":235,"left":228,"right":234,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":16,"right":227,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":227,"left":210,"right":226,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":210,"left":17,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":205,"right":208,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":205,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"le